{"type": "article", "id": 13769, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-20T07:49:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12074, "name": "口红"}, {"id": 14798, "name": "皮革设计"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 12826, "name": "厨房用品"}, {"id": 1326, "name": "茶壶"}, {"id": 5673, "name": "面包机"}, {"id": 14799, "name": "Apple Watch 保护壳"}, {"id": 2961, "name": "Karl Lagerfeld"}, {"id": 14800, "name": "Tiffany Cooper"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133847mspbBF2ln59PNDVT.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tCollection by Karl Lagerfeld &amp; Tiffany Cooper \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>老佛爷和著名漫画家 Tiffany Cooper ，还有...老佛爷的猫 Choupette “联手”推出的卡通饰品系列终于要来了，这个系列包括 T 恤、鞋子、包袋、手机壳等产品，漫画家 Tiffany Cooper 巧妙地取材自老佛爷和他的爱猫 Choupette，他们一起漫游世界，一起吃冰淇淋，一起扮鬼脸，一起搞怪，诙谐的卡通形象里面是一个充满奇思妙想的时尚世界。这个系列将于下个月在日本开卖，感兴趣的可以持续关注。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215342df6SwzNosn3EZ09a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215343aZHoJij2hGtry4SU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215343RcTDqh85I3XpvxmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215344bVH36uYrIcOJGXs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tKitchen Appliances by Naoto Fukasawa for Muji\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>设计师 Naoto Fukasawa 为 Muji 推出了一套厨房用品，包括一个茶壶和一个烤面包机。遵循其一贯的极简设计路线，两件产品都采用原白色，外观上采用圆形的设计，开关等设计在产品的同一面，并进行极简化的处理，看上去憨态可掬。两件产品刚刚登陆美国市场，并将于 11 月份登陆英国市场，明年扩展到全欧洲。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215344pKG2W3cwTOnuxD4N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215345sNOjoGhWVkA4b68m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215345xJT3pDnYVBjM80wm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153468mTsawb74lphPVLI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215350LdiMAvpBXe1ankEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215351ipTRjBZonSbrlxeL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215351hE9NFR21tqPaTpsw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153527YWXSNl5jn1ETo6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215353sWwYN0ICVDUeQOcu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tCase For Apple Watch by Catalyst \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Catalyst 最近推出了一款防水 Apple Watch 保护壳，采用混合塑胶的橡胶材质，可以保证手表在 1 米的水深处仍然可以保证良好的防水性能，同时，产品搭配了一个可以快速拆卸和安装的 24 毫米 NATO 尼龙表带。三种款式分别名为 “Stealth Black”，“Rescue Ranger”，“Green Pop” ，这是<a href=\"http://www.catalystlifestyle.com/collections/frontpage/products/preorder-catalyst-apple-watch-42mm\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215353HYOgmqbvzFtQdERN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215354hRmCsTjXE0IFiaO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215354NyJ87t59fuElIo2K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215355ReYw5KOSoM0QgNAX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153563V1nuilT4fAbmGM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215356cIyMbaqmhFrv3t15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215357JkHl2rayB4LVScX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tComical Lighting Design by Ingo Maurer \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>德国设计师 Ingo Maurer 从上个世纪 60 年代开始就致力于奇思妙想的灯具和照明设计，今年他推出了四款有趣的灯具，其中，“what we do counts” 看上去像是一个大大的平面漫画，而 “i ricchi poveri – monument for a bulb” 的灯座上有许多小人，像在为灯泡立碑，“lucellino” 像是一个飞翔的鸟，而 “walking bulb” 的 LED 灯则不停地进行着水平的 360 度翻转，似乎是在向前走一样。<a href=\"http://www.ingo-maurer.com/de/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215358zuaFONBvlKRCWhQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215402VZu3K1r9TGICcWld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215402MRAdq3gTX7mZoQ2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74105263\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052154052681NPgCBbEGKcTZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052154069fiyE1cVMWJ0TNxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414575EWHDMbIFdkr3zlO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141458MpFV8ztoNhbiGLgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78728606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215406DbrGMmau02gFBLWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215407cWXjGeDw30KCYnBg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73105134\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215407R9vqEgCYe3AKNnTG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141458T215Fmxfj8RdQXar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10268949\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tOne Off Goods by Dino Sanchez \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Dino Sanchez 一直以来因为其极简的木质设计产品著名，最近他将涉及领域扩展到了皮革领域，推出了一系列皮革设计产品，包括钥匙扣、钱包、卡包、笔记本包等等，他把在木材设计中的极简风格延续，注重设计的细节和质感。Dino Sanchez 表示，每一件产品都是独一无二的。<a href=\"http://www.dinosanchez.com/oneoffgoods\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052154080SMxdIvJXKP8w1RW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215408XzZOAMRfKcrqyope.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215409Vi6S7L5ftNUODrMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215409obaT0wN912qhDWRL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052154100kaHbvzgDnWTf8AC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tLipstick by Christian Louboutin\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>近日，红鞋底 Christian Louboutin 进军美妆界推出的口红终于来了，和他们之前推出的指甲油包装一样，经典的 “Louboutin 红色”采用子弹头黑色包装，而其他颜色使用金色包装，目前一共有 38 种颜色，一共有三种质地，分别是光泽缎面、丝绒哑光和薄纱哑光。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215410PuDb721t4WUTsxVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2002924\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215411K8C7nxlO5YN4BmcZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052154111kBiWsNAZGtuca3K.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66129032\" data-format=\"gif\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}